<html lang="en" class="h-100">
  <head>
    <%- include('../../partials/head'); %>
  </head>
  <body class="" style="background-color: #fafafa; padding-bottom: 80px;">
    <div
      style="
        padding-top: 30px;
        background: #1488cc; /* fallback for old browsers */
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(
          to top,
          #2b32b2,
          #1488cc
        ); /* Chrome 10-25, Safari 5.1-6 */
        background: linear-gradient(
          to top,
          #2b32b2,
          #1488cc
        ); /* W3C, IE 10+/ Edge, Firefox 16+, Chrome 26+, Opera 12+, Safari 7+ */
      "
      class="px-3"
    >
      <h3 style="font-weight: 700; padding-left: 20px; color: white">
        📈 SKKOSS
      </h3>
      <div class="pt-2 pb-5">
        <%- include('../../partials/balance', {balance: "50,000"}) %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="px-3" style="padding-top: 30px">
      <h4 style="font-weight: 500; padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px">
        관심 종목
      </h4>
      <%- include('../../partials/card', {data: {name: "수기이노텍", id:
      "sugi"}} ) %> <%- include('../../partials/card', {data: {name: "인의전기",
      id: "ine"}} ) %>
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="display: none">
        <symbol id="check-circle-fill" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path
            d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0zm-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"
          />
        </symbol>
        <symbol id="info-fill" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path
            d="M8 16A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16zm.93-9.412-1 4.705c-.07.34.029.533.304.533.194 0 .487-.07.686-.246l-.088.416c-.287.346-.92.598-1.465.598-.703 0-1.002-.422-.808-1.319l.738-3.468c.064-.293.006-.399-.287-.47l-.451-.081.082-.381 2.29-.287zM8 5.5a1 1 0 1 1 0-2 1 1 0 0 1 0 2z"
          />
        </symbol>
        <symbol
          id="exclamation-triangle-fill"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
        >
          <path
            d="M8.982 1.566a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566zM8 5c.535 0 .954.462.9.995l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995A.905.905 0 0 1 8 5zm.002 6a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2z"
          />
        </symbol>
      </svg>
      <div class="alert alert-primary d-flex align-items-center" role="alert">
        <svg
          class="bi flex-shrink-0 me-2"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Info:"
        >
          <use xlink:href="#info-fill" />
        </svg>
        <div>각 종목을 누르면 세부 정보를 볼 수 있어요!</div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-danger d-flex align-items-center" role="alert">
        <svg
          class="bi flex-shrink-0 me-2"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          role="img"
          aria-label=Danger:"
        >
          <use xlink:href="#exclamation-triangle-fill" />
        </svg>
        <div>
          구매를 결정하시면 하단의 “주문” 버튼을 통해 주식을 구매할 수 있습니다!
          (단, 주문까지 제한 시간은 10분)
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex fixed-bottom">
      <div
        class="timer text-center py-3 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"
        style="width: 30%; font-size: 13px; background-color: white;"
      >
        <p style="margin: 0" class="timer"></p>
      </div>
      <div style="width: 100vw">
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary py-3 rounded-0"
          disabled
          onclick="location.href='/onboarding/info6'"
          style="width: 100%"
        >
         주문
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/timer.js">
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
